languages.text: "Страх оказаться использованн{mf|ым|ой}... Все мы его испытываем. Но чем больше мы можем предложить — тем он сильнее".
"The fear of being used... We all have it. But the more we have to give, the stronger it grows."

languages.text: “害怕被利用……也是人之常情，而且付出得越多，就越害怕。”
languages.original_text: "The fear of being used... We all have it. But the more we have to give, the stronger it grows."

languages.text: «El miedo a que te utilicen... Todos lo tenemos. Pero cuanto más tengamos que ofrecer, mayor será ese miedo».
languages.original_text: "The fear of being used... We all have it. But the more we have to give, the stronger it grows."

languages.text: « La peur que l'on se serve de nous... Nous la connaissons tous, mais plus nous possédons de choses qui peuvent être exploitées, plus cette crainte se renforce. »

languages.text: "Die Angst, benutzt zu werden ... die haben wir alle. Aber je mehr wir zu geben haben, desto stärker wird sie."
languages.original_text: "The fear of being used... We all have it. But the more we have to give, the stronger it grows."

languages.text: 「利用されることへの恐れ…私たちは皆それを持っている。しかし、与えなければならないものが多ければ多いほど、それは強くなる」

languages.text: "Kullanılma korkusu... Hepimizin içinde var. Fakat kaybedecek ne kadar çok şeyimiz varsa bu korku da o kadar büyüyor."
